00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:46,560
I wonder if

217
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:48,000
she's going to let me get out.

218
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:50,600
I'm going to give it a go.

219
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,640
Bear with me on this.

220
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:20,200
- WHISPERS:
- Well, well, well, well, well!

221
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,840
How beautiful is that?

222
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:36,720
She can smell me. My scent is going straight ahead.

223
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,760
She knows I'm here.

224
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,240
She's not bothered at all.

225
