687
00:54:48,080 --> 00:54:50,280
They are very sensitive to heat.

688
00:54:50,280 --> 00:54:55,720
And so as climate change and the habitat changes for them,

689
00:54:55,720 --> 00:54:57,440
they're going to move upslope.

